</div><!-- title -->

<div class="container">

<div class="main">

<div class="content">

<p class="lead">King&#8217;s treat many different types of cancers. We&#8217;re a specialist centre for haemato-oncology, neuro-oncology and liver cancer. We are also a regional centre for breast and bowel cancer screening.</p>

<ul class="list--cols--three">
<li><a href="javascript:void(0)">Anal</a></li>
<li><a href="javascript:void(0)">Bile ducts</a></li>
<li><a href="javascript:void(0)">Bladder</a></li>
