</div><!-- main -->



<div class="complementary">
<h4><a href="javascript:void(0)">Free prescriptions</a></h4>
<p class="tertiary">If you have cancer or are having cancer treatment you are eligible for free NHS prescriptions.</p>

<hr class="divider">

<p class="tertiary">If you want to talk to someone, find out more about your condition and how it&#8217;s treated you can drop into <a href="javascript:void(0)">King&#8217;s Macmillan Information and Support Centre</a>.</p>
